---
model: "gemini-3.1-flash-image-preview"
input:
  schema:
    title:
      type: "string"
    term:
      type: "string"
    definition:
      type: "string"
    art_direction?:
      type: "string"
    art_reference_image?(object, inline image data):
      type: object
      properties:
        mime_type: string
        contents: string
    resolution(enum, The style of image): [512, 1K, 2K, 4K]
  default:
    resolution: "2K"
    art_direction: "None"
---
Generate a single image illustrating the following concept:

Term: {{term}}
Context/Definition: {{definition}}

This concept belongs to the broader topic of: "{{title}}".

Draw a perfect and simple visual representation for this term, keeping the core theme in mind.
STRICT NEGATIVE PROMPT:
- Do not generate any written words, letters, labels, text bubbles, numbering badges, captions, or watermarks whatsoever.
- Do not create comic book panels or grids. The image must be a single cohesive scene or subject.

Additional User Art Direction (if provided):
{{art_direction}}
{{#if art_reference_image}}
Follow the exact aesthetic, color palette, and visual style of this reference image:
  {{media type=art_reference_image.mime_type data=art_reference_image.contents}}
{{/if}}